## How to Use This Document

1. During daily V2 operations, note any friction, repeated actions, or manual work.
2. Record each observation in the log above.
3. After sufficient data is collected (30–90 days), review before resuming V3 development.
4. Use observations to adjust the V3 roadmap in `39_V3_REVIEW_AND_REVISIONS.md`.

